0:{"buildId":"0o__w1-b4jSplRARKjvkd","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","main",null,{"className":"pb-16 text-brand-ink","children":["$","section",null,{"className":"px-4 py-12 sm:py-16","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"page-shell","children":["$","article",null,{"className":"max-w-3xl mx-auto","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"text-xs sm:text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-brand-ink/50","children":"Guide / 2026 报税"}],["$","h1",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold leading-tight","children":"2026 最新 OPT 报税 Form 8843 填写保姆级教程（含 STEM 延期说明）(附 PDF 下载)"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-6 text-lg text-brand-ink/80 leading-relaxed","children":["对于在美留学生尤其是处于 OPT 或 STEM 延期阶段的同学来说，2026 年报税季最基础也最关键的一份文件就是 ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"Form 8843"}],"。 无论你 2025 年是否有收入，只要你依然被定义为 ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"F1 Non-resident"}],"（非居民），这份表就是你的“身份保命符”。"]}],["$","$L2",null,{}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-pink max-w-none mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold mt-12 mb-6 text-brand-ink","children":"为什么 F1/OPT 必须重视 Form 8843？"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-brand-ink/75 leading-7","children":["很多人会问：“我去年一整年都在找工作，没有任何收入（W2/1099），我也要报税吗？” 答案是肯定的。Form 8843 全称是 ",["$","em",null,{"children":"Statement for Exempt Individuals and Individuals with a Medical Condition"}],"。 它的核心作用不是报钱，而是",["$","strong",null,{"children":"声明豁免身份"}],"。"]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-brand-ink/75 leading-7 mt-4","children":"通过这份表，你是在向 IRS 说明：虽然我在美国待的天数可能符合“实质居住测试（SPT）”，但因为我是持 F1 项目的学生， 按照税法规定，我的天数不应计入判定，我依然可以维持 Non-resident 身份，享受学生专属的税务优惠。"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold mt-12 mb-6 text-brand-ink","children":"2026 报税的核心判定逻辑：你是第几年？"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"rounded-[20px] bg-brand-pink/10 p-6 my-6","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-brand-pinkdeep mb-2","children":"五年规则（5-Year Rule）"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-brand-ink/80","children":["F1 学生在美的前 5 个“日历年”通常被视为 Exempt Individual。 比如你是 2021 年入境，那么 2021, 2022, 2023, 2024, 2025 这五年你都是 Non-resident。 即使你在 2025 年进入了 ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"STEM 延期"}],"，只要没超过 5 年，你依然需要填 8843。"]}]]}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold mt-12 mb-6 text-brand-ink","children":"手把手教你填 2026 最新 Form 8843"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"my-8 flex justify-center","children":["$","$L3",null,{"src":"/images/form-8843-sample.webp","alt":"IRS Form 8843 Sample for 2025 Tax Year - Official Statement for Exempt Individuals and Individuals with a Medical Condition","width":1200,"height":1600,"className":"rounded-2xl border border-brand-pink/30 shadow-lg"}]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-brand-ink/75","children":["Form 8843 分为几个部分，学生（F/J/M/Q）通常只需要关注 ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"Part I"}]," 和 ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"Part III"}],"。"]}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4","children":"Part I: General Information"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-brand-ink/75","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Name & Address:"}]," 填写你目前的住址，通常是美国地址。"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"SSN/ITIN:"}]," 如果你有 OPT 收入通常会有 SSN；如果没有收入且没有 SSN，这一项可以留空。"]}]]}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4","children":"Part III: Students"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-brand-ink/75","children":"这一部分是针对 F1 / OPT 同学的核心："}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-brand-ink/75","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Line 9:"}]," 填写你 2025 年入境时的签证类型（F-1）。"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Line 10:"}]," 填写你的 F-1 身份类别（学生）。"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Line 11-12:"}]," 填写你的学校信息、联系人（通常是学校的 DSO）。"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Line 14:"}]," 统计近几年的居住天数。这是防止你被误认作 Resident 的关键项。"]}]]}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold mt-12 mb-6 text-brand-ink","children":"OPT 与 STEM 延期的特殊情况：1040-NR 与 Treaty"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-brand-ink/75 leading-7","children":["如果你在 OPT 或 STEM 延期期间有工资收入，除了 8843，你还需要叠加 ","$L4","。"]}],"$L5","$L6","$L7","$L8","$L9"]}],"$La"]}]}]}]}],["$Lb"],"$Lc"]}],"loading":null,"isPartial":false}
